			<h2 class="post-title"><a href="http://getglennmobile.com/2012/03/23/happy-anniversary/" rel="bookmark">Happy Anniversary?</a></h2>	
	<div class="post-date">
		<p class="day"><a href="http://getglennmobile.com/2012/03/23/happy-anniversary/" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to Happy Anniversary?">Mar 23</a></p>
	</div><!-- .post-date -->

	<div class="post-info clear-block">
		<p class="author alignleft">Posted by <a href="http://getglennmobile.com/author/libertyonwheels/" title="Posts by Glenn Horowitz" rel="author">Glenn Horowitz</a></p>
	</div><!-- .post-info clear-block" -->

	<div class="entry clear-block">
		<p>Wow, it slipped my mind, but just over 6 years ago on March 16 2006, I was diagnosed with MS.</p>
<p>I guess I can&#8217;t be all that surprised, I was already well on my way in my headlong plunge down the rabbit hole at that time.</p>
<p>Tell ya what&#8230;the sooner I can get mobile again, the sooner I can escape <em>that </em>particular dark place. Still working on some promotional help, it&#8217;s slow going but I know it&#8217;ll pay off in the end once my liberty is restored!</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration:underline;color:#0000ff;"><span style="text-decoration:underline;">Bitcoin Donation Address:</span></span><span style="color:#0000ff;"> 1N9FWbFhTQrmTTQwMYYMBoc4ymdXBKSg5L</span></p>
